summary: POPO coin - In the digital realm of Memeville, there lived a legendary figure known as Popo, the buffed Pepe. Unlike his famous predecessor, Popo was muscular and strong, with a determined look in his eyes. His chiseled physique and confident demeanor made him a symbol of strength and resilience. Popo's journey began when he decided to transform himself, dedicating countless hours to self-improvement and fitness. His transformation inspired the residents of Memeville, showing them that with hard work and determination, anyone could achieve greatness.
